lost_found_details.additional_information: She is a 8 year old tabby cat. Very distinctive feature on her is her nose. It is half black and half white. She responds to Angel. Last seen on 112 street between 107 and 109 avenue. She has a flea collar around her neck that is white but she may have taken it off. Very friendly cat.
